               <code code="34071-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="WARNINGS SECTION"/>
               <title>WARNINGS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">KEEP THIS AND ALL DRUGS OUT OF THE REACH OF CHILDREN.</content> In case of accidental overdose, seek professional assistance or contact a Poison Control Center immediately.</paragraph>
